description.p:
(i) To enable adhesive transfer of 100% of the toner image formed on the photoconductor of the photosensitive drum to the adhesive layer of the intermediate transfer member;


(ii) To enable retransfer of 100% of the toner image transferred to the adhesive layer to the final support; and


(iii) When the processes of (i) and (ii) are conducted two or more times, to enable the same adhesive layer to be used repeatedly in the multiple operations.
